Description: # criapi
        
        An API to get cricket scores,scorecards and commentary in python.
        
        ## Installation
        
        Install it as below:
        
        ```bash
        pip3 install criapi
        ```
        
        ## Usage
        
        ### Initialization 
        
        ```python
        from criapi import Cricbuzz
        c=Cricbuzz()
        ```
        
        ### live scores
        
        ```python
        print(c.livescore())
        ```
        
        ### scorecard
        
        ```python
        print(c.scorecard(id))
        ```
        
        ### commentary
        
        ```python
        print(c.commentary(id))
        ```
        
        
        
        
        
